                            <comment id="14464534" author="paulk" created="Tue, 15 Apr 2008 18:14:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;behavior now the same as native launcher&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14464764" author="jopaki" created="Sun, 18 May 2008 11:50:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems now with this change, the global CLASSPATH is not being honored as my shell scripts that append the global CLASSPATH no longer work when upgrading from 1.5.4 to 1.5.6.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So how to I tell groovy of the global classpath now?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14478149" author="paulk" created="Sun, 18 May 2008 17:15:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;CLASSPATH should be passed through to Groovy&apos;s classloading infrastructure just not in the START_CLASSPATH.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14464823" author="paulk" created="Sun, 18 May 2008 17:17:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I meant STARTER_CLASSPATH&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
